{"tid":2072954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：「國安公署」將不會受《基本法》第22條規管 國安顧問如港英時代政治部顧問 國安法凌駕香港法律","createTime":"2020-06-21T03:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T13:05:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":35,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"74e36a759d14480cb8c803334595aa5412bc05bb","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"至於罰則，<span style=\"color: red;\">譚耀宗說，港區國安法沒有罪行會判終身監禁</span>，草案條文對分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、恐怖活動，以及勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全4類犯罪行為有清晰界定，罰則根據案情嚴重程度決定，案情輕微的監禁3年，其他則監禁5至10年。<br />\n<br />\n根據《說明》，港區國安法草案有6章、共66條，分別為：總則；特區維護國安的職責和機構；罪行和處罰；案件管轄、法律適用和程序；中央人民政府駐港維護國家安全機構；以及附則。說明又提到，若香港本地法律與港區國安法不一致時，則按後者規定，而國安法的解釋權屬人大常委會。<span style=\"color: red;\">譚耀宗表示，港區國安法是中央立法，與香港法律層次不同，有凌駕性</span>。他指出，今次常委會並未就港區國安法法律草案作表決，意味尚要開多至少一次會議。<br />\n<br />\n工委的說明指國安法將規定設立健全的維護國安相關機構和職責（見上圖），其中包括中央在港設立「維護國家安全公署」，職責包括：監督、指導、協調、支持香港履行維護國家安全的職責；收集分析國家安全情報信息；依法辦理危害國家安全犯罪案件。有了解北京政策的消息人士表示，在一國兩制下，<span style=\"color: red;\">駐港國安公署的地位與中聯辦類似，直屬中央政府，即不受《基本法》第22條規管</span>。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗稱，國安委員會的秘書長是香港人，現時未有人選，<span style=\"color: red;\">而國安顧問會是「中央的人」</span>。被問到該名顧問是否「太上皇」，他說國安是中央負責的事，有些個案相當複雜，要靠中央提供資料，設立顧問有利協調和溝通等。<span style=\"color: red;\">政府消息人士表示，國安顧問類似港英時代「政治部」（Special Branch）的政治顧問</span>，好處是一起合作下可建立中央與香港的互信、理解，不用中央每每出手。"},{"pid":"f9e9b16b8bf32ac674b0118faa83837f11547043","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045733c11a54d97a107d7c3e49e82437a696b36e","tid":2072954,"uid":51583,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:53:43.000Z","msg":"最緊要立得夠過份<br />\n外國先可以做更多野<br />\n最終有一日都係走架啦"},{"pid":"548ee945cebc5d9e2a502c502d55c3a0b2939d9a","tid":2072954,"uid":53003,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:54:41.000Z","msg":"67暴動 &rarr; ICAC<br />\n反送中運動 &rarr; 國安公署<br />\n厲害了我的国👍"},{"pid":"101ea7ab9b9b97dbc8b8157e5c3abe6452cedfea","tid":2072954,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:54:58.000Z","msg":"殖民者"},{"pid":"57e45285ea1e8035bf73b1b4f6f32382ee218854","tid":2072954,"uid":6752,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"咪即係香港市<br />\n得啦搞咁多野"},{"pid":"3426e9a18cfb032cc84a2e82177849f2fa5d8288","tid":2072954,"uid":127575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"快D立啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a12339e814ffd0d70b419f90b4924c264b25446","tid":2072954,"uid":148355,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"咪撚縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09162c4b2768eaae8be62d51774182fa511057c","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548ee945cebc5d9e2a502c502d55c3a0b2939d9a","tid":2072954,"uid":53003,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:54:41.000Z","msg":"67暴動 &rarr; ICAC<br />\n反送中運動 &rarr; 國安公署<br />\n厲害了我的国👍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f39d9f51a42cd3c7100aede7b83ae904dfd7a4","tid":2072954,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07875a42819fdd66a41294832ea95065f374f33f","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:59:18.000Z","msg":"了解北京政策的消息人士稱，公署有權辦案的「特殊情况」主要是國家層面的重大案件，例如：<span style=\"color: red;\">假設有涉及伊斯蘭國或國家國土問題案件，又或是內地重要國安案件的疑人逃到香港</span>，香港警察未必有足夠情報或能力處理，屆時或要由中央出手處理。"},{"pid":"93cc7f381a8f9b5c2fa9ae50ed5e8cc8f0e1f04b","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>消息：涉國土問題或內地逃犯 中央或出手</strong><br />\n另有政府消息人士說，有信心香港能處理大部分國安案件，惟可能有一些案件，<span style=\"color: red;\">例如國家國安部門正跟進的重大案件</span>，國安公署比較熟悉，他們自己處理會好過由香港處理；<span style=\"color: red;\">另外一些涉及國際的重大案件如間諜案</span>，香港警察亦未必有能力處理，可能要由公署的人員跟進。該官員說，上述案件甚少在香港出現，但也不能排除會出現，故中央留有一手是可理解的。"},{"pid":"88da638c8fe082b477fa0fa769bdbba9bfaed954","tid":2072954,"uid":21470,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"中聯辦都凌駕22條啦"},{"pid":"6ad1340d98950d9ed86f45aa62768fc4e85a2c5b","tid":2072954,"uid":205927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"基本法已廢"},{"pid":"43d777265806f336f62f14ec3fa7f765fc3f49cf","tid":2072954,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"07875a42819fdd66a41294832ea95065f374f33f","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:59:18.000Z","msg":"了解北京政策的消息人士稱，公署有權辦案的「特殊情况」主要是國家層面的重大案件，例如：<span style=\"color: red;\">假設有涉及伊斯蘭國或國家國土問題案件，又或是內地重要國安案件的疑人逃到香港</span>，香港警察未必有足夠情報或能力處理，屆時或要由中央出手處理。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:02:01.000Z","msg":"錫克廟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527673be3d1f156a7df4bba2ac0da18905034a3b","tid":2072954,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"Deadbody?"},{"pid":"5264ea7041d4fae2388fc00ea5af8e95ab984064","tid":2072954,"uid":53062,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"一次過推翻廿二條 廿三條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0931ab51c27b629061fba50fb1f3bb60ff12e1","tid":2072954,"uid":46534,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"咁第二十二條立嚟為乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80e8c5390742354d8483e3545a1ec1c48b9413d","tid":2072954,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"88啦基本法"},{"pid":"6a5ec0cf14ea010e317f379cf8df1e1167e02c65","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d246bc02a77ba7e4336e2d541b0789f45bca7f","tid":2072954,"uid":185507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0c3b0b1499a13139aa1b1a79f7d5326cbd14c8e","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f13bf4280cbf212052ee0ee308b2454bb4a00f","tid":2072954,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e36a759d14480cb8c803334595aa5412bc05bb","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"至於罰則，<span style=\"color: red;\">譚耀宗說，港區國安法沒有罪行會判終身監禁</span>，草案條文對分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、恐怖活動，以及勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全4類犯罪行為有清晰界定，罰則根據案情嚴重程度決定，案情輕微的監禁3年，其他則監禁5至10年。<br />\n<br />\n根據《說明》，港區國安法草案有6章、共66條，分別為：總則；特區維護國安的職責和機構；罪行和處罰；案件管轄、法律適用和程序；中央人民政府駐港維護國家安全機構；以及附則。說明又提到，若香港本地法律與港區國安法不一致時，則按後者規定，而國安法的解釋權屬人大常委會。<span style=\"color: red;\">譚耀宗表示，港區國安法是中央立法，與香港法律層次不同，有凌駕性</span>。他指出，今次常委會並未就港區國安法法律草案作表決，意味尚要開多至少一次會議。<br />\n<br />\n工委的說明指國安法將規定設立健全的維護國安相關機構和職責（見上圖），其中包括中央在港設立「維護國家安全公署」，職責包括：監督、指導、協調、支持香港履行維護國家安全的職責；收集分析國家安全情報信息；依法辦理危害國家安全犯罪案件。有了解北京政策的消息人士表示，在一國兩制下，<span style=\"color: red;\">駐港國安公署的地位與中聯辦類似，直屬中央政府，即不受《基本法》第22條規管</span>。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗稱，國安委員會的秘書長是香港人，現時未有人選，<span style=\"color: red;\">而國安顧問會是「中央的人」</span>。被問到該名顧問是否「太上皇」，他說國安是中央負責的事，有些個案相當複雜，要靠中央提供資料，設立顧問有利協調和溝通等。<span style=\"color: red;\">政府消息人士表示，國安顧問類似港英時代「政治部」（Special Branch）的政治顧問</span>，好處是一起合作下可建立中央與香港的互信、理解，不用中央每每出手。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"分裂國家、顛覆國家政權未必係叛國<br />\n恐怖活動，以及勾結外國或者境外勢力係叛國<br />\n<br />\n國家安全=政府安全"},{"pid":"46e7ff3349c7fc300b00f08ca9ca06c9534d67ce","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276be4272edfbbdd50951eb592cc833836bd4ed9","tid":2072954,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f12b1545bb5a85058a6e2f849f735a1fecb9c7","tid":2072954,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ec5a831bd03c84fdf9c69ca1d7eac42fdab867","tid":2072954,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"CKGB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acacbe3f18daa176b462454706039805365bd681","tid":2072954,"uid":7343,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"50f12b1545bb5a85058a6e2f849f735a1fecb9c7","tid":2072954,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41c244db5494ea83423b77fdb1a1d5437419b1c","tid":2072954,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2